history.content: I won't comment on your chances for 170, but regarding Data 100 we'll probably accommodate people with final conflicts. We'll clarify official policy later on as it's still TBD

Currently, I'm enrolled in my maximum units for Phase 1 and 1.5, but I would also like to take Data 100 in the fall. However, Data 100 has a time conflict with another course that I'm taking, so even though it allows time conflicts, I'm not sure if I'd be able to take the final. In addition, signing up for Data 100 would mean that I drop CS170 (I'm position 300) and re-add it in phase 2. Is there a chance of getting CS170 with being around 450 on the waitlist, and who do I contact for final conflicts in Data 100?
history.subject: Data 100 Time Conflicts
